comments: Abolished 1.4.1934 and added to the parish of Grimsargh.
Abolished 1894 and added to the parish of Preston.

Created 1.4.1934 out of the parishes of Grimsargh with Brockholes 
    and Elston. See also Table 2, note (b).

Abolished 1.4.1934 and divided between the parishes of Grimsargh 
    and Preston.

That part which until 1.4.1934 formed part of the parish of Walton-le-Dale. 
    See also Table 2, note (b).

Abolished 1.4.1934 and divided between the parishes of Penwortham 
    and Lea.

Created 1.4.1934 out of the parishes of Lea Ashton Ingol & Cottam, 
    Grimsargh with Brockholes, Hutton and Howick. See also Table 2, note (b).

Abolished 1.4.1934 and divided between the parishes of Lea, Fulwood, 
    Penwortham and Hutton.

That part which until 1.4.1934 formed part of the parish of 
    Samlesbury. See also Table 2, note (b).

Abolished 1.4.1974 and added to the Preston unparished area. See also Table 
    2, notes (c), (d) and (e).

Abolished 1.4.1934 and divided between the parishes of Preston 
    and Fulwood.
